OL,3,CWarnings Welsh homes will go cold this
OL,4,Cwinter as price cap increases by 10%
OL,6,FThere are warnings that households in
OL,7,FWales will go cold this winter, as
OL,8,FOfgem announces a 10% increase to the
OL,9,Fenergy price cap.
OL,11,FOfgem's energy price cap will increase
OL,12,Ffrom #1,568 to #1,717 from October 1
OL,13,Ffor a typical household in England,
OL,14,FScotland and Wales, the regulator has
OL,15,Fannounced.
OL,17,FAhead of Ofgem's announcement on the
OL,18,FEnergy Price Cap, the Bevan Foundation
OL,19,Fwarned that people will go cold this
OL,20,Fwinter.
