OL,3,CWarnings Welsh homes will go cold this
OL,4,Cwinter as price cap increases by 10%
OL,6,FOfgem, the regulator, sets the price
OL,7,Flimit based on several factors
OL,8,Fincluding wholesale energy prices `
OL,9,Fthe amount energy firms pay for gas
OL,10,Fand electricity before supplying it to
OL,11,Fhouseholds. It is updated every three
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FIt means households could be going
OL,15,Finto the colder months facing higher
OL,16,Fbills than they have had from April
OL,17,Fthis year, when the price cap was
OL,18,Flowered.
