OL,3,CWarnings Welsh homes will go cold this
OL,4,Cwinter as price cap increases by 10%
OL,6,FJoel Davies, Policy and Research
OL,7,FOfficer at the Bevan Foundation said
OL,8,F"energy supplier schemes can and do
OL,9,Fmake a real difference to people
OL,10,Fstruggling financially, but we have
OL,11,Ffound that some people are missing out
OL,12,Fon this vital lifeline.
OL,14,F"It is important to make sure that low-
OL,15,Fincome households are receiving all
OL,16,Fthe help they can get."
OL,18,FThe Foundation says it can be hard to
OL,19,Ffind out about the help that energy
OL,20,Fcompanies offer, and that applying to
OL,21,Fthe schemes is not always easy.
