OL,6,FThey say application deadlines are
OL,7,Fsometimes brought forward as suppliers
OL,8,Fhave used their budget, eligibility
OL,9,Fcriteria can be unclear and dealing
OL,10,Fwith call centres is often a real
OL,11,Fchallenge.
OL,13,F"Even if someone does get help, it is
OL,14,Fnot always enough to make a real
OL,15,Fdifference. Too often, people are left
OL,16,Fwith nowhere to turn, just because
OL,17,Fthey've fallen into energy arrears at
OL,18,Fthe wrong time."
