OL,6,FThe Bevan Foundation say there are
OL,7,Fsteps that should be taken to improve
OL,8,Fthe current system, such as requiring
OL,9,Fenergy suppliers to make their schemes
OL,10,Fmore accessible and easier to apply
OL,11,Ffor. Looking to the longer term, the
OL,12,FFoundation says that action is needed
OL,13,Fto improve the help provided by
OL,14,Fsuppliers and to make sure that the UK
OL,15,FGovernment ensures that everyone has
OL,16,Fenough to cover the cost of everyday
OL,17,Fessentials such as energy.
