OL,3,CWarnings Welsh homes will go cold this
OL,4,Cwinter as price cap increases by 10%
OL,6,F"The Welsh Government needs to step up
OL,7,Fits investment in the energy
OL,8,Fefficiency of Wales' housing stock,
OL,9,Fand energy suppliers, Ofgem and the UK
OL,10,FGovernment must work together to
OL,11,Fimprove the affordability of energy
OL,12,Fprices for low-income households."
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government spokesperson says
OL,15,F"we will invest #30m to improve home
OL,16,Fenergy efficiency in lower income
OL,17,Fhouseholds again this year, and we are
OL,18,Falso working with local authorities to
OL,19,Fhelp people take advantage of the GB-
OL,20,Fwide ECO Flex scheme in Wales.
